org.gbif.registry.ws.model

Class LegacyEndpointResponse

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.gbif.registry.ws.model.LegacyEndpointResponse

  • public class LegacyEndpointResponse
extends Object
    Class used to generate responses for legacy (GBRDS/IPT) API.
    JAXB annotations allow the class to be converted into an XML document or JSON response. @XmlElement is used to specify element names that consumers of legacy services expect to find.
